_json.gridTitle: SPCAI Provides Support For Military Pets & Their Caretakers
_json.description: ~Donate to Operation Baghdad Pups!  Without Operation Baghdad Pups, a majority of service members could not afford to bring their special companions home from the Middle East. Your donations will help us provide soldiers with travel crates, vaccinations, transportation for their animal to the Baghdad Airport & transport home.  http://www.spcai.org/index.php/programs/operation-baghdad-pups.html  Please, help today! Donations of $, leashes, collars, food & water dishes. etc. HELP TODAY PLEASE!
